    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: portraits.Array.size
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: sentences.Array.size
      value: 16
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[0]'
      value: hello
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[1]'
      value: Isn't it a beautiful day?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[2]'
      value: Yes, it's nice...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[3]'
      value: Huh? You seem very distracted lately, is something wrong?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[4]'
      value: ...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[5]'
      value: Roland...I'm pregnant...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[6]'
      value: huh..?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[7]'
      value: HUH!!!!!????
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[8]'
      value: ' I... didn''t know how to tell you... I, sr-'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[9]'
      value: That's wonderful!! How great, how wonderful! I can't wait! Will it be
        a boy or a girl? What will we name it? Will it like fencing like its father?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[10]'
      value: '*laughing* You are so dumb'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[11]'
      value: I was afraid of how you would react, to be honest, but now I realize
        that I'm the fool for doubting you.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[12]'
      value: How could I not be happy? After these months I was dying to know. I'm
        glad you told me despite your fear; you're very brave.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[13]'
      value: Whatever... thanks Roland, well I'm going to request the withdrawal
        from the department, finally we have all the savings for a quiet and free
        life, in a few months they will give me my maternity leave
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
